## Modifications

NthLayer uses these templates as-is with the following customizations:
- Service-specific labels added (service, team, tier)
- Runbook URL annotations added
- Notification channel annotations added
- Templates filtered by service tier

The original alert expressions and thresholds are preserved.

## Usage in NthLayer

NthLayer loads these templates and customizes them for specific services,
but does not claim ownership of the original alert definitions.

All generated alerts include attribution to awesome-prometheus-alerts.

